"title": "2369: Jesus Christ, responses to",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2369: jesus christ, responses to",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The NT records a number of responses to Jesus Christ on the part of those who encountered him, both positive and negative.</p>\n<h2>Negative responses to Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Rejection</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:42\">MAT 21:42</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:5-Mark7:8\">MRK 7:5–7:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:28-Luke4:30\">LUK 4:28–4:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:16\">LUK 10:16</a></p>\n<h3>Lack of faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:4-Mark6:6\">MRK 6:4–6:6</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:57-Matt13:58\">MAT 13:57–13:58</a></p>\n<h3>Questioning his authority</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:27-Mark11:33\">MRK 11:27–11:33</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:23-Matt21:27\">MAT 21:23–21:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:1-Luke20:8\">LUK 20:1–20:8</a></p>\n<h3>Hardening of hearts</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:10-Matt13:17\">MAT 13:10–13:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:37-John12:41\">JHN 12:37–12:41</a></p>\n<h3>Attributing his power to satanic forces</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:33-Matt9:34\">MAT 9:33–9:34</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Demanding his death</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:20-Luke23:24\">LUK 23:20–23:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:22-John10:40\">JHN 10:22–10:40</a></p>\n<h2>Positive recognition of Jesus Christ's identity</h2>\n<h3>As Messiah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:41\">JHN 1:41</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:11\">LUK 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:20\">LUK 9:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:42\">ACT 5:42</a></p>\n<h3>As King</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:49\">JHN 1:49</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:1-Matt2:2\">MAT 2:1–2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:37\">MAT 27:37</a></p>\n<h3>As Lord</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:68\">JHN 6:68</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:13\">JHN 13:13</a></p>\n<h3>As Son of David</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:22\">MAT 15:22</a></strong></p>\n<h3>As Son of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:20\">ACT 9:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:29\">MAT 8:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:34\">JHN 1:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:49\">JHN 1:49</a></p>\n<h3>As Teacher</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:16\">MAT 19:16</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:17\">MRK 10:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:18\">LUK 18:18</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:10\">MAT 23:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:28\">JHN 11:28</a></p>\n<h2>Responses to Jesus Christ by those whom he healed</h2>\n<h3>Faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:52\">MRK 10:52</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:42\">LUK 18:42</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:13\">MAT 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:27-Matt9:31\">MAT 9:27–9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:43-John4:54\">JHN 4:43–4:54</a></p>\n<h3>Thankfulness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:11-Luke17:19\">LUK 17:11–17:19</a></p>\n<h3>Witnessing to others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:38-Luke8:39\">LUK 8:38–8:39</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:40-John1:42\">JHN 1:40–1:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:45-John1:46\">JHN 1:45–1:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:10-John5:15\">JHN 5:10–5:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:13-John9:34\">JHN 9:13–9:34</a></p>\n<h2>Responses to Jesus Christ by those whom he met and taught</h2>\n<h3>Amazement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:26-Matt7:29\">MAT 7:26–7:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:17\">MRK 12:17</a></p>\n<h3>Delight</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:37\">MRK 12:37</a></p>\n<h3>Faith</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:10\">MAT 8:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:2\">MAT 9:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:22\">MAT 9:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:28\">MAT 15:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:11\">JHN 12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:41-John12:43\">JHN 12:41–12:43</a></p>\n<h3>Repentance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:8\">LUK 19:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:20\">MAT 11:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:12\">MRK 6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:2-Luke13:5\">LUK 13:2–13:5</a></p>\n<h3>Obedience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:20\">MAT 28:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:20\">JHN 15:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:6\">JHN 17:6</a></p>\n<h3>Worship</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:2\">MAT 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:33\">MAT 14:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:9\">MAT 28:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:52\">LUK 24:52</a></p>\n<h2>Responses to Jesus Christ by those whom he redeemed</h2>\n<h3>Faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:31\">ACT 16:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:9-Rom10:10\">ROM 10:9–10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:23\">1JN 3:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:5\">1JN 5:5</a></p>\n<h3>Obedience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:26\">ROM 16:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:12\">PHP 2:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:8-Heb5:9\">HEB 5:8–5:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:17\">1PE 4:17</a></p>\n<h3>Calling on his name</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:14\">ACT 9:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:21\">ACT 9:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:13\">ROM 10:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:2\">1CO 1:2</a></p>\n<h3>Giving thanks in his name</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:20\">EPH 5:20</a></p>\n<h3>Glorifying his name</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:12\">2TH 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>Proclaiming him to the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:42\">ACT 5:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:5\">ACT 8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:10\">ACT 16:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:19\">ROM 15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:28\">COL 1:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:8\">2TI 1:8</a></p>",
